--- Descriptor Score Parameters: Grid Score ---
descriptor_grid_score_rep_rad_scale                          1
descriptor_grid_score_vdw_scale                              1
descriptor_grid_score_es_scale                               1
descriptor_grid_score_grid_prefix                            grid

--- Descriptor Score Parameters: Pharmacophore ---
descriptor_fms_score_use_ref_mol2                            yes
descriptor_fms_score_ref_mol2_filename                       reference.mol2
descriptor_fms_score_write_reference_pharmacophore_mol2      no
descriptor_fms_score_write_reference_pharmacophore_txt       no
descriptor_fms_score_write_candidate_pharmacophore           no
descriptor_fms_score_write_matched_pharmacophore             no
descriptor_fms_score_compare_type                            overlap
-------------------------------------------------------------
You are using a ligand based reference for computing the FMS.
When the value is 0 then there is a perfect overlap.
When the value is negative then you have multi-matched ph4.
When the value is positive then you have matches with residual.
-------------------------------------------------------------
descriptor_fms_score_full_match                              yes
descriptor_fms_score_match_rate_weight                       5.0
descriptor_fms_score_match_dist_cutoff                       1.0
descriptor_fms_score_match_proj_cutoff                       0.7071
descriptor_fms_score_max_score                               20

--- Descriptor Score Parameters: Fingerprint / Tanimoto ---
descriptor_fingerprint_ref_filename                          ligand.mol2

--- Descriptor Score Parameters: Hungarian Matching Similarity ---
descriptor_hms_score_ref_filename                            ligand.mol2
descriptor_hms_score_matching_coeff                          -5
descriptor_hms_score_rmsd_coeff                              1

--- Descriptor Score Parameters: Volume Overlap Score ---
descriptor_volume_score_reference_mol2_filename              ligand.mol2
descriptor_volume_score_overlap_compute_method               analytical

--- Descriptor Score Weights ---
descriptor_weight_grid_score                                 1
descriptor_weight_pharmacophore_score                        1
descriptor_weight_fingerprint_tanimoto                       1
descriptor_weight_hms_score                                  1
descriptor_weight_volume_overlap_score                       1

Using these settings, the Descriptor Score function takes the form:
Descriptor_Score = (1 * Grid_Score) + (1 * Pharmacophore_Similarity_Score) + (1 * Tanimoto) + (1 * Hungarian_Matching_Similarity_Score) + (1 * Volume_Score)

